1. *Znajući* da će biti kiše, ponela je kišobran. (Knowing that it would rain, she brought an umbrella.)
2. Ponela je kišobran, *znajući* da će biti kiše. (She brought an umbrella, knowing that it would rain.)
3. *Znajući* da neće uspeti sam, tražio je pomoć. (Knowing that he wouldn't succeed alone, he asked for help.)
4. Tražio je pomoć, *znajući* da neće uspeti sam. (He asked for help, knowing that he wouldn't succeed alone.)
5. *Znajući* da je danas ponedeljak, odlučila je da ode u teretanu. (Knowing that today is Monday, she decided to go to the gym.)
6. Odlučila je da ode u teretanu, *znajući* da je danas ponedeljak. (She decided to go to the gym, knowing that today is Monday.)